Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tendron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Flanchet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Quasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:20:00.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tendron! Quasi! Collier!\NFlanchet! Cuisseau! Jarret!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:03.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tendron! Quasi! Collier!\NFlanchet! Cuisseau!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Collier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:15.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jarret! Collier! Quasi!\NFlanchet! Gigot! Selle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Queue! Jarret! Collier! Quasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Flanchet! Gigot! Selle! Queue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Queue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Veau Shot!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=5}=================SANJI ATTACK END===================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ho perso...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:55.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Assurdo... respiri ancora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:22:00.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Che c'è? Se ti trasformassi \Nnuovamente in Nami,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,non riuscirei a darti il colpo di grazia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:06.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ridicolo. Non riesco più a muovermi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:09.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,che senso avrebbe evitare la fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:13.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hai... vinto tu. Uccidimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}In ogni caso, il mio destino... mi porterebbe \Nad essere eliminato dall'organizzazione.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Perché perdi tempo?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dammi il colpo di grazia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:34.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È stato un grande scontro. \NNon dovrebbero servire altre parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:48.89,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Questa è... senza dubbio... \Nla prova dell'amicizia tra due rivali...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:51.22,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ma io... non piangerò!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:58.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ciao! Mi riprendo gli \Nocchiali del nostro cecchino!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.80,0:23:01.78,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Me lo ha dato... il colpo di grazia...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:09.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Di nuovo... qualche osso è andato, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:26.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Qui siamo pronti!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Anche qui possiamo \Npartire in ogni momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:39.98,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2\t(5219,5990,1,\c&HFCFDFB&\3c&HFCFDFB&\4c&HFCFDFB&)}Questo castello... \Nha visto quattromila anni... di storia di Alabasta.{Cora}{avevate perso il typesetting gente, state attenti pls -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:48.43,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Era il mio orgoglio...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:54.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ma... distruggendo il palazzo reale,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}il popolo smetterà di combattere e ascolterà!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:02.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Riuscirò a dirgli la verità con le mie parole!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Forza! Accendete il fuoco!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:07.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Questo è...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:27.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tutto bene?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.54,0:24:31.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,L-Lui è...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:35.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Questo sarebbe un problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:50.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Che brutte maniere, Miss Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.21,0:24:54.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Questa presto sarà la mia casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.84,0:24:56.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:00.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vostra Maestà!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.79,0:25:01.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Padre!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.41,0:25:07.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Proprio bello, eh? Il palazzo reale.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:14.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Un luogo perfetto per guardare \Ndall'alto quegli inutili plebei.{Chara}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.70,0:25:17.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dov'è Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.45,0:25:24.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eh? Quel "Cappello di Paglia"? \NQuel novellino scadente?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.09,0:25:29.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lui...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.25,0:25:31.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,è morto!
